{"tid":168411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦恐襲：兇手英國出生　IS承認責任","createTime":"2017-03-23T13:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T04:57:38.000Z","uid":82646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d64158c9eeb3edf40b65856d4a8a6dbe9d39a10b","tid":168411,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/photo/bknint-20170323175121041-0323_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170323204605\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170323%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170323175121041-0323_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170323204605&h=2f606e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撞擊國會大閘的兇徒（上圖）於英國出生，而IS（下圖）事後承認責任。（美聯社／資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n英國國會恐襲發生後，國會一度關閉。事隔一日後，國會周四重開，並舉行了一分鐘的默哀儀式，悼念遇難的死者。首相文翠珊於國會上亦發表了演說，指：「面對恐襲，我們仍然無懼！」她續指，行兇者在英國出生，更曾經因其極端暴力行為而受到情報部門軍情五處（MI5）監視；極端回教組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）事後承認責任。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊在國會上強調英國無懼恐襲，稱民眾如常生活就是對恐怖主義的最大反擊；又大派「定心丸」指，現時未有任何證據顯示英國會受到更嚴重的襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n她又透露，現時送院的傷者來自11個國家，當中包括12名英國人、3名法國人、4名南韓人、1名中國人、1名意大利人及1名美國人等。而英女王伊利沙伯二世亦於周二指，對事件表示遺憾，形容自己的「禱告及深切慰問」會與所有受影響的人同在。<br />\n<br />\n另外，蘇格蘭議會發言人表示，議會將於下周二下午2時20分，辯論由蘇格蘭首席部長施雅晴提出的獨立公投草案，預料草案可在議會通過。蘇格蘭議會原本打算於下周啟動脫歐程序前，表決是否再度舉辦獨立公投。有議員周三對表決延遲初時表示不滿，但在得悉倫敦襲擊的詳情後贊同決定，認為是尊重的表現。<br />\n<br />\nfrom on cc <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/bknint-20170323175121041-0323_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170323%2Fbknint-20170323175121041-0323_17011_001.html&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=9c4de6a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/bknint-20170323175121041-0323_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a5c42d854c549494ad3905683f94b117c5295f43","tid":168411,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"啲人真係養唔熟"},{"pid":"0d4b976b6948e9420dec4d326f8bdae96aae120e","tid":168411,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"19 才子又加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23317feaa2a97f834c81af694d42f2ebcd2f4e74","tid":168411,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:23:58.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得就算唔係, isis都會衝出黎認左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa3dfc1bcf26d1f9cc0bd2905ea1982fc4720c6","tid":168411,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e97bbead03aea1f617dacf50bc4a87989a7883d6","tid":168411,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬係覺得就算唔係, isis都會衝出黎認左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有傷亡咪認囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前襲擊機場同羅浮官，<br />\n人都傷唔到個就畀人一槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果d咁水皮咁瘀咪唔認囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2142a92577195b8cab8eec5d786b10611f6b535d","tid":168411,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>19 才子又加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個算唔算?<br />\n因為唔係難民</blockquote><br />\n唔算"},{"pid":"e85aaf4c2088a53585fc573ddd66e5283dd457cf","tid":168411,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:12:26.000Z","msg":"侵侵又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 左膠又點睇？"},{"pid":"0bc505113922bc24e7d7e5068d57f6c978b0dea9","tid":168411,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"係唔係都認左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}